==Azerbaijani==
{{az-variant|c=јарпаг|a=یارپاق}}
[[File:Lisc lipy.jpg|thumb|{{uxi|az|Cökə '''yarpağı'''|A linden '''leaf'''}}]]
===Etymology===
Ultimately from {{inh|az|trk-pro|*yapurgak|t=leaf}} <ref>{{R:tut-pro:SDM|*japur-gak|url=http://starling.rinet.ru/cgi-bin/response.cgi?single=1&basename=%2fdata%2falt%2fturcet&text_number=46&root=config}}</ref>. Developed through [[w:metathesis|metathesis]], compare {{cog|tr|yaprak}}. However, this phonological process has not occurred for all words in all dialects (see below). Cognate with {{cog|tt|яфрак}}, etc.
===Pronunciation===
